{"tid":1511504,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"揸車既巴絲 呠柒啲警車！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T15:50:12.000Z","uid":35584,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b82f206d180897d1c582528aab45f4737a1da303","tid":1511504,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:22:27.000Z","msg":"每次揸車係馬路見到警車都要呠柒佢地！<br />\n係前面又好 係隔離線都好 <br />\n呠柒佢地！！！！<br />\n見到幾耐就呠幾耐！！<br />\n香港警察淪落過街老鼠！！！<br />\n十點大叫都可以遍地開花<br />\n呢樣都可以！"},{"pid":"28a512a1c35640c619238ef11a69f03284dad79d","tid":1511504,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f19ec0845319efcc00e1237bf67a13db5dc68239","tid":1511504,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf48dada7962cf3f04f15278529b86dfddea1354","tid":1511504,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"348b20ac71603b3c5155850b7411d385a7d5a386","tid":1511504,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:24:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2df2494e06ce75d3d6935be1e3d07fbf2765343","tid":1511504,"uid":302878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"對面線我直頭舉中指"},{"pid":"4fb282eb4d64838c3b8aca1617a4abe440835ee8","tid":1511504,"uid":154992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:25:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20141019/s00001/1413669547560/%E9%9F%BF%E8%99%9F%E6%92%90%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E7%A5%A8%E6%8E%A7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20141019%2Fs00001%2F1413669547560%2F%25E9%259F%25BF%25E8%2599%259F%25E6%2592%2590%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%258E%25A7&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=cdc38e13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20141019%2Fs00001%2F1413669547560%2F%25E9%259F%25BF%25E8%2599%259F%25E6%2592%2590%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%258E%25A7&h=ae269569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20141019/s00001/1413669547560/%E9%9F%BF%E8%99%9F%E6%92%90%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E7%A5%A8%E6%8E%A7</a><br />\n<br />\n響號撐佔領 司機被票控 (06:34)<br />\n2014/10/19<br />\n<br />\n 共3幅 下一頁  上一頁<br />\n大批市民仍然在彌敦道北行線近恆生銀行對開聚集，與警方對峙。其間，多次有駛經車輛響號支持，留守者則鼓掌歡呼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但至凌晨4時許，一輛客貨車經過並響號時，被警員截停並以「無故響號」為由，票控定額罰款。隨後兩輛私家車經過響號，同樣被警員截停，記下車主及車牌號碼，並作口頭警告。<br />\n<br />\n其間，有在場佔領人士不滿，大聲批評警方選擇性執法，警員遂作出口頭警告，要求有關人士不要再煽動別人。但半分鐘後，有一名灰衣男子高呼「走啦，呢度唔歡迎啲差人」，隨即有警員上前把灰衣男鎖上手扣，帶上警車。"},{"pid":"84e0e39cac93bb6c15dd5ebc00db5bfd3751fcc2","tid":1511504,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14cf4199f1113cacc122ca3e7b819bd70e4b636","tid":1511504,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:27:40.000Z","msg":"過街老鼠！！！"},{"pid":"bd31106f60d440790153f371fc0b8e7cebb230dc","tid":1511504,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"亂響安 落車就拉你啦<br />\n無車牌叫人去死"},{"pid":"b1e47455d38b0ffaa8ece9a2dded986b3a01d6c3","tid":1511504,"uid":45305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:29:46.000Z","msg":"每次都想屌9佢地<br />\n但好怕佢地會放狗咬人"},{"pid":"3b2c78452a9658b4eabb05b5c7b56bf20d5e2b4f","tid":1511504,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84e0e39cac93bb6c15dd5ebc00db5bfd3751fcc2","tid":1511504,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"【升級罷工全民自決】<br />\n一名打工仔為升級罷工決策考慮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511688</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yi8wPfF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYi8wPfF.jpg&h=e926e235&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akg2VVG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fakg2VVG.jpg&h=1780cd27&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}